  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot, sauté onion, carrot, and celery in 1 tablespoon of oil until soft.",
    "Add potato, vegetable broth, thyme, and salt. Bring to a boil, then reduce heat and simmer for 20 minutes until potato is tender.",
    "Add rye bread slices and simmer for 5 minutes to soften.",
    "Stir in Dutch process cream and sugar until smooth and creamy. Simmer gently for 3 minutes.",
    "Adjust seasoning with salt and pepper to taste. Serve hot."
